# Local-only secrets for `vite dev` / `wrangler dev`. Copy to `.dev.vars`
# and fill in real values. Never commit `.dev.vars`.
#
# Phase 2+ placeholders:
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
# OPENAI_API_KEY=
#
# Bearer token for the company-picker stock search (POST /api/stock/search,
# proxies devde.muns.io). Without it the picker reports "not configured".
# MUNS_ACCESS_TOKEN=
